# Project Guidelines (Claude Code)

This project follows Spec-Driven Development (SDD). The canonical rules live in the submodule.
Read these before any work:

@vendor/ai-sdd-guide/rules/core.md
@vendor/ai-sdd-guide/rules/workflow.md
@vendor/ai-sdd-guide/rules/subagents.md
@vendor/ai-sdd-guide/rules/conventions.md

- Design phases (spec/plan/tasks/verify): Claude only. Use superpowers and subagents.
- Implementation: any agent. Treat `specs/<feature>/` as a contract — follow it exactly.
- Human-facing docs: `vendor/ai-sdd-guide/docs/` / Templates: `vendor/ai-sdd-guide/templates/`
- Hooks: copy `integration/settings.json.example` to `.claude/settings.json`.
- Subagents: copy `integration/agents/` to `.claude/agents/`.

(If you change the submodule path, update the references above to match.)
